<node id="&quot;DIAPHRAGM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Diaphragm is an inspiratory muscle involved in the breathing process, particularly important during exhalation for controlling respiratory pressure."&lt;SEP&gt;"The diaphragm is a muscle that plays a crucial role in breathing, relaxing and returning to its resting position after inhalation.")&lt;SEP&gt;"diaphragm is a muscle that plays a crucial role in breathing, contracting to draw air into the lungs during inhalation."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5d75b6e35d99dd76cf7cf11d5dd4c669&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a50f580c4d4e704c505f145305237334&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6</data>
