<node id="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental body or agency that has the authority to issue orders or enact laws."&lt;SEP&gt;"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental body that could be notified due to non-compliance with laws or policies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Governmental Entity refers to any governmental organization that may provide funding or support to the Company or its Subsidiaries."</data>
