<node id="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Transactions refer to specific actions or agreements that the Company is involved in, such as mergers, acquisitions, or restructuring."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to specific business activities or agreements that are subject to certain conditions for completion."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to specific business activities or agreements that the Company and its subsidiaries are involved in, as outlined in the Definitive Documents."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transactions refer to the actions or agreements that are subject to the conditions and representations in the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fab095535ef654128190466b5b23d787&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89615f4ec46bbdd23718896275864ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5818a7090ee1170819f4ec743fb6ce29</data>
