</node>
<node id="&quot;DEFINITIVE DOCUMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Definitive Documents are documents that may affect the ability of Supporting Lenders to enforce rights and remedies under certain agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are formal agreements or contracts that outline the terms and conditions of a transaction or project."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are formal agreements or contracts that outline the terms of a transaction or agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are formal agreements or contracts that outline the terms of the transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are key documents related to the Restructuring process, which must comply with the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are legal agreements or documents that outline specific transactions or terms, including the Restructuring Term Sheet and this Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are the final and binding documents that outline the terms and conditions of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents refer to formal agreements or contracts that outline the terms of transactions or restructuring plans."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents refer to legal agreements or contracts that outline the terms of the Transactions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5818a7090ee1170819f4ec743fb6ce29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-328e8bc9e087c28dbed85b191eb5cadc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fab095535ef654128190466b5b23d787&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89615f4ec46bbdd23718896275864ce9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2981e34156c10752a2b073a41fc40757&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da883cb7464aa2b0304c0a5e2752a2ee</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 34}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 79}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Company is a business entity that owns assets and operates in various jurisdictions, requiring qualification in those areas."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a legal entity that has entered into an agreement with Supporting Lenders and provides representations and warranties to them."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a musical staged in 1970 by Stephen Sondheim in partnership with Harold Prince."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a party to the Agreement and is involved in the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is an organization that will accept the form and substance of the credit agreement.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity filing motions and requests related to the Restructuring process, including extending exclusive periods to file the Plan and solicit acceptances."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity that Supporting Lenders can consult with, but their ability to do so may be restricted."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity undergoing reorganization and recapitalization through the Chapter 11 cases."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the business entity that owns and operates IT assets and is subject to data privacy and cybersecurity regulations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is involved in the Transactions and is undergoing Chapter 11 bankruptcy proceedings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is involved in the transactions and is subject to certain conditions for completing them."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is making certain conditions and representations in a legal agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity mentioned in the text, which is subject to various security policies and contractual obligations regarding Personal Information."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity whose certificate of incorporation and bylaws are being discussed, along with its subsidiaries and their equity interests."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main organization mentioned in the text, which has established and implemented Privacy and Security Policies since January 1, 2017."</data>
