  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lenders are a specific group of parties under the Agreement, agreeing to certain terms and conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are entities that provide support or financing and are making certain representations in the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities providing support to the Company as outlined in the Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that have provided or will provide support to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide support or funding for a specific agreement or project."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or entities that provide support or funding for the transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties involved in agreements that give rise to claims or interests, and their rights and interests may be affected by certain actions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties involved in the Restructuring process, having specific rights and obligations as outlined in the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to an agreement with the Company and receive certain disclosures from the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to the Agreement and are involved in the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the entities entitled to receive the Expense Reimbursement Amount as per the Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the financial backers of the company mentioned in the context."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the financial institutions or entities that are entitled to receive the Expenses Reimbursement Amount from the Debtors."</data>
