<node id="&quot;VOCAL MECHANISM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vocal Mechanism encompasses the physical and functional aspects of the voice production, including the vocal folds and the different registers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Vocal Mechanism is the physical structure responsible for producing sound in the human voice."&lt;SEP&gt;"Vocal mechanism refers to the anatomical structures involved in producing sound, including the vocal folds, resonators, and breathing muscles."</data>
