<node id="&quot;CANNON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cannon is a medical officer who served during a significant battle, handling numerous casualties and witnessing the aftermath of the conflict."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a medical officer who successfully treated several soldiers with sodium bicarbonate, leading to their recovery."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a medical professional who advocated for and implemented procedures to prevent shock in wounded soldiers, organizing 'shock teams' and inspecting their performance in battle."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cannon is a military officer who achieved rapid promotions during the war and was recognized for his services."</data>
