  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Control refers to the ability to manage or govern, which is challenged by an intelligence that writes its own rules."&lt;SEP&gt;"Control refers to the ability to manage or govern, which is challenged by an intelligence that writes its own rules."|&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The concept of Control is challenged by the Intelligence that writes its own rules."&lt;SEP&gt;"The concept of Control is relevant to the idea of First Contact, as it involves managing and understanding an unknown entity."</data>
