  <data key="d2">chunk-517c563bb28c6e8e2284f65f24dada91</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BROADWAY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Broadway is a famous street in New York City known for its theaters and theatrical productions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Broadway is the famous theater district in New York City where many of these musicals were produced and performed."&lt;SEP&gt;"Broadway is the main stage for musical theater productions in New York City, experiencing significant changes in the late 1960s and early 1970s."&lt;SEP&gt;"Broadway is the street in New York City where the double bill _The Black Domino/Between You, Me and the Post_ was performed in 1866."&lt;SEP&gt;"Broadway was the main street in New York City where many of Laura Keene's productions were staged, particularly 'The Elves' and 'The Seven Sisters'."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeb961c56fad5bba709f67c784ce1fa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-193b8e1e9f10173a42ef43aa5d5f0dd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 0}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 20}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;_HAIR_&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"_Hair_ is a rock musical produced in 1968, known for its experimental and innovative style and praised by critics for its authentic voice."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aeb961c56fad5bba709f67c784ce1fa4</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;_HELLO DOLLY_&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"_Hello Dolly_ is a long-running musical from the previous era, still enjoying success in the late 1960s."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aeb961c56fad5bba709f67c784ce1fa4</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;_FIDDLER ON THE ROOF_&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
