  <data key="d2">chunk-aeb961c56fad5bba709f67c784ce1fa4</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LONG RUNS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Long Runs refer to the extended performances of established musicals like _Hello Dolly_ and _Fiddler on the Roof_, which continued to be successful despite the changes in the industry."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-aeb961c56fad5bba709f67c784ce1fa4</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRANSITION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
