<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated companies of the Debtors, involved in the restructuring plans and agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the same corporate umbrella as the Company, sharing similar data privacy and cybersecurity responsibilities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are companies wholly or partially owned by the Company and are part of the same corporate group."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are organizations that are part of the Company, sharing the same Privacy and Security Policies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are owned by the Company and are mentioned in relation to their equity interests and obligations under various agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations of the Company, also subject to the same security policies and contractual obligations regarding Personal Information."</data>
