<node id="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Debtors are organizations that intend to file petitions commencing the restructuring process.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors are the companies or entities that are undergoing restructuring plans and have associated plans or agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors are the entities filing the Chapter 11 cases, which include the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to parties that owe money or have financial obligations, typically mentioned in the context of legal commitments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the entities involved in the Chapter 11 Case, responsible for paying the Expense Reimbursement Amount as per the Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the parties involved in a financial agreement, responsible for paying the Expense Reimbursement Amount as per the terms of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the parties that owe money or have some kind of financial obligation to the Company."</data>
