<node id="&quot;BANKRUPTCY COURT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bankruptcy Court is the court in the Northern District of Texas where the Chapter 11 Cases will be filed."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court is the court that will approve the Disclosure Statement Order."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court is the judicial body that oversees the bankruptcy proceedings and must approve the Disclosure Statement Order for the Debtors' obligations to become binding."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court is the judicial body that will approve the Disclosure Statement and Solicitation Materials."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court is the judicial body where hearings related to the Chapter 11 Cases are held."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court is the organization that will enter the DIP Orders in form and substance mutually acceptable to the Company and the DIP Agent.")</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-56d6447d6158799fdf295d41c7cc0f30&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65a82af78e8e41a2d20ae5cb6529c57c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71e5b5184b7ec9d75dd60420b76b39c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bf97277dd4f00a2f3ba0aec7d182864&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7cf50994b52751855b1afce08fc2fcd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ec3e0c9650042a5eb8ae3d17cf7e4ce</data>
