</node>
<node id="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Laura Keene is a theatrical producer who staged eight musicals and toured with her troupe after closing her New York City theater due to financial difficulties."&lt;SEP&gt;"Laura Keene was a pioneering actress and manager who achieved national success and recognition, known for her innovative theatrical productions such as 'The Elves' and 'The Seven Sisters'."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
