</node>
<node id="&quot;AUDIENCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Audiences were the primary consumers of theatrical productions, seeking entertainment and distraction from the challenges of daily life."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 15}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 70}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 110}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRANSFORMATION SCENE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A transformation scene was a unique feature of 'The Seven Sisters', where the entire stage set changed in full view of the audience, demonstrating advanced theatrical techniques."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 15}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 70}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 113}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PATRIOTIC FANTASY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Patriotic fantasy was a theme used in 'The Seven Sisters', blending elements of American patriotism with theatrical spectacle."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 15}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 70}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 113}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FINANCIAL PANIC&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A Financial Panic occurred in New York City after the war, which affected the theater industry."&lt;SEP&gt;"A financial panic occurred in New York City after the Civil War, affecting the theater industry and leading to a brief period of economic instability."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
