</node>
<node id="&quot;OLD QUEEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Old queen is the existing queen in the hive that the new queen will replace."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-581be0c6c7e8fcfca682a8b090ad02dc</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PACKAGE CONTAINER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Package container is a device used to transport bees, containing a queen and worker bees, often used in beekeeping operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Package container is a temporary housing for bees during transportation or relocation, designed to protect and contain the bees."</data>
