  <data key="d6">chunk-3659761488646fddbeb1aaccb780f32c</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;EXCLUSIVE PERIODS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company has the right to extend its exclusive periods to file the Plan and solicit acceptances thereof, but these actions must be consistent with the agreement and the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PLAN ACCEPTANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company is responsible for initiating the Plan and soliciting acceptances thereof, and Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan if it does not comply with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;LEGAL PROCEEDINGS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company cannot take any actions where such taking would be inconsistent with the agreement, the Restructuring Term Sheet, or the Definitive Documents, or otherwise inconsistent with, or reasonably expected to prevent, interfere with or impede the implementation or consummation of, the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">370.0</data>
  <data key="d5">The Company and its Supporting Lenders are integral to the Restructuring process. The Company is responsible for filing motions and requests, while the Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject certain documents, ensuring that their actions are consistent with the Restructuring process. Both entities are also entitled to participate as parties in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process. The Supporting Lenders can consult with the Company, although their ability to do so may be limited during the Effective Period. The Company provides or will provide information to the Supporting Lenders, likely for financial or legal purposes. Additionally, the Company makes conditions and representations that apply to the Supporting Lenders, and both entities are parties to the Agreement, which outlines the terms and conditions for the Restructuring process. The Supporting Lenders have the right to object to or vote to reject any motions filed by the Company that are consistent with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process.</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5818a7090ee1170819f4ec743fb6ce29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fd38d91626796c5dd8e495df3c6af46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69dadc79d0bd793c8236311babc87f2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fab095535ef654128190466b5b23d787&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2981e34156c10752a2b073a41fc40757</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;EFFECTIVE DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">48.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are bound by the conditions and representations that take effect on the Effective Date."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders must perform their obligations at or prior to the Effective Date."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders' obligations are subject to the satisfaction of conditions at or prior to the Effective Date."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da883cb7464aa2b0304c0a5e2752a2ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5818a7090ee1170819f4ec743fb6ce29</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
