<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;RESTRUCTURING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">78.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Restructuring is a process that can affect the Supporting Lenders' obligations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have specific rights and obligations related to the Restructuring process, including the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object to or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object to or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object to or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object to or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the agreement, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5de4506ebf12460c924336c672dfa5b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
