<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;">
  <data key="d4">102.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Restructuring Term Sheet provides details that will influence the decision of the Supporting Lenders regarding the Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the Restructuring Term Sheet, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the Restructuring Term Sheet, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the Restructuring Term Sheet, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process, and they have the right to appear as a party in legal proceedings related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the Restructuring Term Sheet, and they cannot take actions inconsistent with the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the right to object or vote to reject the Plan or Definitive Documents if they do not comply with the Restructuring Term Sheet."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are bound by the Restructuring Term Sheet that outlines the terms of a restructuring plan or agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-69dadc79d0bd793c8236311babc87f2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b71af048d4f8dc28e13f8005b181437&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5818a7090ee1170819f4ec743fb6ce29</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
