  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Journey is the event during which the package and bees travel from the beeyard to their destination."&lt;SEP&gt;"The journey involves the package and bees traveling from the beeyard to their destination."&lt;SEP&gt;"The package undergoes a traumatic journey north, involving various modes of transportation and exposure to extreme conditions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ccf5e4489055ac80e4d05a0eafbf7b20</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
