  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Screening is used to separate the new queen from the mass of bees in the package."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ccf5e4489055ac80e4d05a0eafbf7b20</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PACKAGE&quot;" target="&quot;QUEEN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The new queen is introduced into the package to lead the bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"The queen is confined in a small cage near the top of the package, ensuring her safety during transportation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccf5e4489055ac80e4d05a0eafbf7b20</data>
