  <data key="d4">44.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"If installation is delayed, the package should be installed in a hive as soon as possible to ensure the survival of the bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Installation is the process of putting the package into the hive to continue the colony's lifecycle."|&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The package needs to be installed in a hive if installation is delayed, ensuring the survival of the bees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-309310970b70cf80a5016a8416c27ab4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293</data>
