  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Acute Promyelocytic Leukemia is a disease characterized by Translocations, which Rowley studied."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSLOCATION&quot;" target="&quot;BURKITT'S LYMPHOMA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Burkitt's Lymphoma is a disease characterized by Translocations, which Rowley and another group studied."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSLOCATION&quot;" target="&quot;GENETIC INSIGHTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Genetic Insights are derived from studying Translocations, which Rowley made significant progress in."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROWLEY&quot;" target="&quot;LEUKEMIA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Rowley conducted research on specific chromosomal changes in leukemia, providing evidence for genetic causes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROWLEY&quot;" target="&quot;ACUTE PROMYELOCYTIC LEUKEMIA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Rowley identified a translocation in Acute Promyelocytic Leukemia, contributing to the understanding of this specific type of leukemia."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROWLEY&quot;" target="&quot;BURKITT'S LYMPHOMA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Another group, possibly collaborating with Rowley, discovered a translocation in Burkitt's Lymphoma, expanding the scope of her research."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHROMOSOMAL CHANGES&quot;" target="&quot;CANCER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Chromosomal changes were initially considered to be far out of reach in terms of understanding their role in cancer."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;CHROMOSOMAL CHANGES&quot;" target="&quot;SKEPTICISM&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Skepticism about the role of chromosomal changes in cancer was prevalent, reflecting the challenges in validating these concepts."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BIOLOGY&quot;" target="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Biology is the field in which Research is conducted, focusing on the study of living organisms and their interactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;" target="&quot;SCIENTIFIC JOURNAL PUBLICATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Scientific Journal Publication is the result of conducting Research, as evidenced by Rowley's work."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;" target="&quot;CAREER SHIFT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Career Shift is a result of dedicating more time to Research, as seen in Rowley's case."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;" target="&quot;BIKING TO LAB&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Biking to Lab is a mode of transportation used to facilitate Research, indicating Rowley's commitment."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cd07e490ccf823a8fb9cd8c3c52b4240</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;" target="&quot;VOCAL ATHLETES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Research on whether healthy belting can be performed weekly is sparse."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-b76cb7a97a0a93c1fb8f78f65cc66f8e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROCKEFELLER INSTITUTE&quot;" target="&quot;PEYTON ROUS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Peyton Rous worked at the Rockefeller Institute and conducted his groundbreaking research there."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROCKEFELLER INSTITUTE&quot;" target="&quot;VIRUS CAUSING SARCOMAS IN CHICKENS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Rockefeller Institute, where Peyton Rous worked, played a crucial role in the discovery of the virus causing sarcomas in chickens."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROCKEFELLER INSTITUTE&quot;" target="&quot;HUMAN DISEASE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Rockefeller Institute's research on viruses causing sarcomas in chickens laid the groundwork for future studies on the role of viruses in human diseases."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ROCKEFELLER INSTITUTE&quot;" target="&quot;MINSTREL SHOWS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"While the Rockefeller Institute focused on scientific research, the cultural context of the time, including minstrel shows, reflects the broader social and cultural landscape of the era."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PEYTON ROUS&quot;" target="&quot;SARCOMAS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Peyton Rous discovered a virus that could produce sarcomas in chickens, linking the virus to the development of these tumors."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PEYTON ROUS&quot;" target="&quot;NOBEL PRIZE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Peyton Rous was awarded the Nobel Prize for his discovery of the virus causing sarcomas in chickens, despite initial skepticism."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PEYTON ROUS&quot;" target="&quot;ELECTRON MICROSCOPY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Electron microscopy contributed significantly to the validation of Peyton Rous's discovery of the virus causing sarcomas in chickens."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SARCOMAS&quot;" target="&quot;VIRUS CAUSING SARCOMAS IN CHICKENS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The virus discovered by Peyton Rous was found to cause sarcomas in chickens, establishing a direct link between the virus and the tumors."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VIRUS CAUSING SARCOMAS IN CHICKENS&quot;" target="&quot;HUMAN DISEASE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Although no such viruses had been identified in humans, the discovery of viruses causing sarcomas in chickens suggested a potential role for viruses in human diseases."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VIRUS CAUSING CANCER IN HUMANS&quot;" target="&quot;ELECTRON MICROSCOPES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Electron microscopes allowed scientists to see viruses in greater detail, contributing to the establishment of the concept of cancer-causing viruses."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VIRUS CAUSING CANCER IN HUMANS&quot;" target="&quot;SKEPTICISM&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Skepticism about the role of viruses in cancer was also prevalent, but the discovery of viruses causing sarcomas in chickens helped to overcome this skepticism."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ELECTRON MICROSCOPES&quot;" target="&quot;TUMOR-CAUSING VIRUSES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Electron microscopes provided visual evidence of viruses, helping to establish their role in cancer."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TUMOR-CAUSING VIRUSES&quot;" target="&quot;TUMOR-CAUSING VIRUSES IN HUMANS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The concept of tumor-causing viruses in humans was initially unclear but was supported by the discovery of similar viruses in animals."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SKEPTICISM&quot;" target="&quot;ROCKEFELLER INSTITUTE'S RESEARCH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The research conducted at the Rockefeller Institute, particularly by Peyton Rous, helped to overcome skepticism about the role of chromosomal changes and viruses in cancer."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ELECTRON MICROSCOPY&quot;" target="&quot;PEYTON ROUS'S DISCOVERY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Peyton Rous's discovery of the virus causing sarcomas in chickens paved the way for further research using electron microscopy."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-708efd6fe2a4d447a789c388f8aeed9b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NEW YORK CITY&quot;" target="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene found success in New York City, a city with a growing and sophisticated population demanding more complex forms of entertainment."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NEW YORK CITY&quot;" target="&quot;THE SEVEN SISTERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Seven Sisters was performed in New York City, highlighting the city's role in hosting groundbreaking theatrical productions during the mid-19th century."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NEW YORK CITY&quot;" target="&quot;CIVIL WAR&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"During the Civil War, theater productions in New York City faced challenges but also opportunities, as actors were given clearance to perform for audiences on both sides of the conflict."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;NEW YORK CITY&quot;" target="&quot;THEATERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Theaters in New York City were crucial for hosting Laura Keene's productions and meeting the entertainment demands of the city's population."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;THE ELVES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene produced 'The Elves', which was the first long-run musical on Broadway, marking a significant achievement in her career."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;THE SEVEN SISTERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene starred in and managed 'The Seven Sisters', a highly successful musical with an unprecedented number of performances, showcasing her innovative approach to theater."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;CIVIL WAR&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Civil War influenced Laura Keene's career, as she continued to produce and manage successful theatrical works despite the broader societal upheaval."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;ACTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene managed and led a troupe of actors, including herself, in producing successful theatrical works."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;NEW YORK CITY THEATER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene operated the New York City Theater before financial difficulties forced her to tour with her troupe."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LAURA KEENE&quot;" target="&quot;FORD'S THEATRE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Laura Keene performed at Ford's Theatre in Washington, D.C., where President Abraham Lincoln was assassinated."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THE SEVEN SISTERS&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSFORMATION SCENE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Seven Sisters featured a transformation scene, a unique theatrical element that showcased advanced stagecraft techniques."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THE SEVEN SISTERS&quot;" target="&quot;PATRIOTIC FANTASY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Seven Sisters incorporated patriotic fantasy as a theme, blending American patriotism with theatrical spectacle."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THEATERS&quot;" target="&quot;FINANCIAL PANIC&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Financial Panic affected the theater industry in New York City, leading to economic instability and impacting the operations of theaters like those where Laura Keene performed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ACTORS&quot;" target="&quot;AUDIENCES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Actors performed for audiences, providing them with entertainment and distraction during challenging times."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;AUDIENCES&quot;" target="&quot;FINANCIAL PANIC&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Financial Panic led to a brief period of economic instability, which likely affected the behavior and preferences of theater audiences in New York City."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c327d240cc02f4086ef379cf45e3feef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
