  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Ford's Theatre is located in Washington, D.C., where President Abraham Lincoln was assassinated."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-7f4321d445729e00164d7f710ea357b9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THE BLACK DOMINO/BETWEEN YOU, ME AND THE POST&quot;" target="&quot;THE BLACK CROOK&quot;">
  <data key="d4">13.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Both events are significant in the development of American theater, with The Black Domino/Between You, Me and the Post using the term 'musical comedy' and The Black Crook being considered the first Broadway musical, despite the claim being disputed."&lt;SEP&gt;"These events occurred within the same year, 1866, and both represent important milestones in the evolution of musical theater in America."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THE BLACK DOMINO/BETWEEN YOU, ME AND THE POST&quot;" target="&quot;AMERICAN THEATER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Black Domino/Between You, Me and the Post represents a significant change in American theater by introducing the term 'musical comedy'."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THE BLACK CROOK&quot;" target="&quot;AMERICAN THEATER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Black Crook marks another significant event in American theater, being considered the first Broadway musical, though the claim is disputed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fb32ce27616da78546076c3f28b79293</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
