  <data key="d4">15.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"American theater and installation are unrelated, but both represent significant developments in their respective fields."&lt;SEP&gt;"Installation and its role in placing the package in a hive are unrelated to American theater, but both represent significant developments in their respective fields."</data>
